{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d3a4a113e5","title":"看了《逼上梁山》以后写给延安平剧院的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"92f6eace3b","index":0,"year":1944,"month":1,"day":9,"articleId":"d3a4a113e5"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","name":"红旗一九六七年第九期","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"《红旗》杂志编辑部","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives2/main/d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"94cad84479","type":"paragraph","text":"看了《通上梁山》以后写给延安平剧院的信","index":0,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"d3a4a113e5"},{"id":"1b9836746d","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九四四年一月九日）","index":1,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"d3a4a113e5"},{"id":"86d3b959a0","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"d3a4a113e5"},{"id":"8cbf465e8d","type":"paragraph","text":"看了你们的戏，你们做了很好的工作，我向你们致谢，并请代向演贸同志们致谢！历史是人民创造的，但在日戏舞台上（在一切离开人民的旧文学旧艺术上）人民却成了造藻，由老爷太太少爷小姐何统治着舞台，这种历史的颠倒，现在由你们再颠倒过来，恢复了历史的面目，从此旧刷开了新生面，所以值得庆贺。你们这个开端将是旧剧革命的划时期的开端，我想到这一点就十分高兴，希望你们多编多演，蔚成风气，推向全国去！","index":3,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"d3a4a113e5"}],"page":{"id":"3dc3ad1789","publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"d3a4a113e5","start":4,"end":4}}}},"__N_SSG":true}